796
00:54:30,310 --> 00:54:31,268
How far have you got?

797
00:54:32,399 --> 00:54:34,706
Well, through his former wife

798
00:54:34,749 --> 00:54:38,057
I tracked him to San Antonio,
but then I ran into a dead end.

799
00:54:38,100 --> 00:54:39,450
He's not there anymore.

800
00:54:39,493 --> 00:54:41,060
Do you know where he worked?

801
00:54:41,103 --> 00:54:42,801
I think he was
an insurance adjuster

802
00:54:42,844 --> 00:54:45,151
for a company called
Transworld Fidelity.

803
00:54:45,194 --> 00:54:46,587
