855
00:57:29,446 --> 00:57:35,364
<i>Yes, we show a John D. Payton</i><i>
insurance adjuster in Tampa</i><i>
at 4682 Ayrshire Drive.</i>

856
00:57:35,408 --> 00:57:37,932
