in Tampa?

857
00:57:37,976 --> 00:57:39,412
<i>Isn't that who you wanted?</i>

858
00:57:39,456 --> 00:57:42,371
Yes. Yes, it is.
Hold on one second.

859
00:57:43,285 --> 00:57:44,809
Give me that address again.

860
00:57:44,852 --> 00:57:48,465
<i>Uh, that's 4682 Ayrshire Drive.</i>

861
00:57:49,553 --> 00:57:52,469
Thank you. Thank you very much.

862
00:57:53,644 --> 00:57:54,645
Whoo!

