931
01:00:55,695 --> 01:00:56,870
Thanks.

932
01:01:01,309 --> 01:01:03,094
Will you take these?

933
01:01:03,137 --> 01:01:04,138
Yeah.

934
01:01:05,487 --> 01:01:07,359
