01:01:38,564 --> 01:01:40,348
Are you sure that it's daddy?

942
01:01:40,392 --> 01:01:42,916
I mean, Thomas Griffin.

943
01:01:43,830 --> 01:01:46,006
Actually, years ago,

944
01:01:48,661 --> 01:01:51,316
