your arrest last year,

1266
01:25:02,227 --> 01:25:05,883
you transferred your share
of co-owned property,

1267
01:25:05,926 --> 01:25:12,542
cash certificates of deposit
and ownership
in a duplex apartment?

1268
01:25:12,585 --> 01:25:15,545
That all belongs to my wife
and her family.

1269
01:25:15,588 --> 01:25:20,637
Didn't you spend more than
$20,000 in home improvements
last year,

1270
01:25:20,680 --> 01:25:23,553
including the purchase
of a wide screen TV

1271
01:25:24,423 --> 01:25:28,253
at a cost of $3200?

1272
01:25:28,297 --> 01:25:31,430
I object, Your Honor.
Really, a television set?

1273
01:25:31,474 --> 01:25:35,260
I am trying to show
that he has been
hiding cash all along.

1274
01:25:36,174 --> 01:25:37,567
Answer the question, Mr. Payton.

1275
01:25:39,090 --> 01:25:40,483
The truth is, Your Honor,

1276
01:25:40,526 --> 01:25:42,833
I'm stone broke
and deeply in debt.

1277
01:25:46,228 --> 01:25:47,707
I don't even have
a bank account.

1278
01:25:49,056 --> 01:25:50,449
Right after Tommy's...

1279
01:25:56,325 --> 01:26:01,547
Right after Mr Payton's arrest,
he and his wife closed

1280
01:26:01,591 --> 01:26:05,116
their money market account
of fourteen thousand dollars.

1281
01:26:05,160 --> 01:26:08,032
And we have canceled checks
from his employers

1282
01:26:08,075 --> 01:26:10,295
for more than $ 30,000.

1283
01:26:10,339 --> 01:26:12,341
LAWYER: Now we're getting
a lesson in accounting.

1284
01:26:12,384 --> 01:26:14,299
Your Honor, I must object.

1285
01:26:14,343 --> 01:26:15,909
Please move it along,
Ms. Bennett.

1286
01:26:17,650 --> 01:26:18,651
Yes, Your Honor.

1287
01:26:35,668 --> 01:26:36,756
One last question.

1288
01:26:38,541 --> 01:26:41,239
You met your daughters,
Andrea and Marcia
for the very first time

1289
01:26:41,283 --> 01:26:42,893
just recently, is that correct?

1290
01:26:43,676 --> 01:26:46,070
No, that is not correct.

1291
01:26:46,113 --> 01:26:48,115
Excuse me.

1292
01:26:48,159 --> 01:26:51,858
For the first time
since Andrea was a baby.

1293
01:26:51,902 --> 01:26:54,513
I don't believe you
ever didn't meet your
daughter Marcia.

1294
01:26:54,557 --> 01:26:55,558
Whatever.

1295
01:27:06,308 --> 01:27:08,048
Do you know who
this young woman is?

1296
01:27:09,441 --> 01:27:11,095
[AMBIENT MUSIC PLAYING]

1297
01:27:16,361 --> 01:27:17,580
No, I don't.

1298
01:27:19,190 --> 01:27:20,409
PAT: That's very sad.

1299
01:27:23,368 --> 01:27:24,369
That's your daughter.

1300
01:27:26,284 --> 01:27:27,329
That's Christine.

1301
01:27:29,156 --> 01:27:31,158
You don't even know who
your own daughter is.

1302
01:27:36,816 --> 01:27:39,950
PAT: Your honor,
this man has not seen

1303
01:27:39,993 --> 01:27:43,823
his children for 17 years.

1304
01:27:44,694 --> 01:27:46,435
He has changed his identity.

1305
01:27:46,478 --> 01:27:50,221
He has committed bigamy
and he has failed
to support his children.

1306
01:27:50,265 --> 01:27:53,703
He has showered
himself with luxuries

1307
01:27:53,746 --> 01:27:56,923
while his children were forced
to live on welfare.

1308
01:27:56,967 --> 01:27:57,968
LAWYER: Your Honor...

1309
01:28:04,670 --> 01:28:07,847
Your Honor, if a man
were brought before you

1310
01:28:07,891 --> 01:28:10,589
who had abused and
beaten his children,

1311
01:28:10,633 --> 01:28:13,288
this court would have
no problem in condemning him.

1312
01:28:15,638 --> 01:28:17,422
While my children may look...

1313
01:28:18,380 --> 01:28:20,338
perfectly healthy

1314
01:28:21,426 --> 01:28:22,688
on the outside,

1315
01:28:24,386 --> 01:28:25,430
but on the inside...

1316
01:28:27,389 --> 01:28:31,044
they are bruised
and scarred for life.

1317
01:28:31,088 --> 01:28:34,352
And there is no amount of money
that is ever going to make up

1318
01:28:34,396 --> 01:28:38,008
for the emotional damage
that has been done to them

1319
01:28:38,051 --> 01:28:40,663
by not having a father
all these years.

1320
01:28:42,969 --> 01:28:47,713
This pattern of allowing men
to simply run away

1321
01:28:47,757 --> 01:28:52,327
from their responsibility
as fathers has got to stop.

1322
01:28:53,545 --> 01:28:55,939
And it could stop right here
and right now,

1323
01:28:55,982 --> 01:28:58,898
if you find this
one father in contempt

1324
01:28:58,942 --> 01:29:01,597
for failure to pay
child support.

1325
01:29:01,640 --> 01:29:03,425
Show these people

1326
01:29:03,468 --> 01:29:05,296
that the system
really does work.

1327
01:29:07,124 --> 01:29:10,083
I want my girls to be able
to walk away from here

1328
01:29:10,127 --> 01:29:13,173
with some sense of dignity

1329
01:29:13,217 --> 01:29:15,350
and some hope
for the future.

1330
01:29:16,220 --> 01:29:18,396
Please, Your Honor.

1331
01:29:21,878 --> 01:29:22,879
Please.

1332
01:29:28,841 --> 01:29:32,628
Hearing the testimony, the court
will take a short recess.

1333
01:29:34,760 --> 01:29:36,588
You'll have my decision
in one hour.

1334
01:29:36,632 --> 01:29:37,633
[KNOCK]

1335
01:29:52,169 --> 01:29:53,170
BAILIFF: All rise.

1336
01:30:17,150 --> 01:30:22,547
Having heard the testimony,
the court finds John Douglas
Payton's failure

1337
01:30:22,591 --> 01:30:27,857
to make payments
of back child support,
willful and premeditated.

1338
01:30:29,641 --> 01:30:33,297
Mr Payton, in addition
to making payments

1339
01:30:33,340 --> 01:30:39,346
of back child support
in the amount of $ 106,500,

1340
01:30:39,390 --> 01:30:42,306
you are remanded
into the custody of the
Pasco County Jail

1341
01:30:42,349 --> 01:30:45,004
for a period of not less
than thirty days.

1342
01:30:46,876 --> 01:30:48,791
Relax, you're not gonna
do any time.

1343
01:30:48,834 --> 01:30:52,795
JUDGE: In addition,
you'll be forced to pay
back interest,

1344
01:30:52,838 --> 01:30:57,843
bringing your total sum of debt
to $146,200.

1345
01:31:01,847 --> 01:31:03,849
Ms. Bennett,

1346
01:31:03,893 --> 01:31:06,852
you're a very brave woman
and an inspiration

1347
01:31:06,896 --> 01:31:09,855
to millions of other women
out there suffering as you have.

1348
01:31:13,293 --> 01:31:14,294
Good luck to you.

1349
01:31:19,256 --> 01:31:20,431
This court is adjourned.

1350
01:31:40,364 --> 01:31:41,496
[ALL CRYING]

1351
01:32:00,602 --> 01:32:04,344
PAT: <i>You know, the pain</i><i>
never really goes away but</i>

1352
01:32:05,258 --> 01:32:06,912
<i>we've learned to live with it.</i>

1353
01:32:08,566 --> 01:32:10,307
<i>Our life is so much better now.</i>

1354
01:32:11,221 --> 01:32:15,617
<i>Somehow resolved, peaceful.</i>

1355
01:32:15,660 --> 01:32:21,318
<i>The girls are growing into</i><i>
wonderful young women</i><i>
right before my eyes.</i>

1356
01:32:21,361 --> 01:32:25,322
<i>And believe it or not,</i><i>
I'm in my second year</i><i>
of law school.</i>

1357
01:32:30,806 --> 01:32:32,764
<i>As for Tommy,</i>

1358
01:32:32,808 --> 01:32:37,464
<i>well, two hours after the</i><i>
hearing, his wife</i><i>
bailed him out of jail.</i>

1359
01:32:37,508 --> 01:32:41,077
<i>Then, four weeks later,</i><i>
he began missing his</i><i>
weekly payments.</i>

1360
01:32:41,120 --> 01:32:45,211
<i>But he caught up quickly</i><i>
when I threatened</i><i>
him with jail again.</i>

1361
01:32:45,255 --> 01:32:49,476
<i>He still sends me and the girls</i><i>
a hundred dollars every week.</i>

